Package: thickness-agent
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Rajdeep Analytics <aadit@rajdeepanalytics.com>
Description: Thickness Agent - CD22 sensor reader and cloud uploader
 Reads CD22 thickness sensors over TCP and uploads readings to the
 Rajdeep cloud server, authenticated per-device. Runs as a service.
